metadata.name: Sunlight & Cello
metadata.description:
Mari started her journey with Mia (The Cello) a while ago - In an afternoor She was practicing and I saw the golden light coming through the window and touching her face, So without telling her just picked up my camera and took some pictures of her picture from the mirror infront of her.
She liked the photos so much, So we decided to do this more often and continue the journey with capturing the moments.
